data.description: Great location! Just inside East Gate around the corner from Balboa Golf Course. This updated one level home features open living area, dining, and kitchen, vaulted ceilings, walk in closets, and fabulous private fenced back yard, crawlspace has encapsulated with heavy-duty vapor barrier and sealed vents. Updates include fresh paint, window treatments, floors and fireplace. This beautiful home comes fully furnished and includes the lot next door. Don't miss this great buy!!
